<DocLayout
  title="agentmako concepts — MCP, context packets, Reef Engine, freshness"
  description="The core concepts behind agentmako — MCP, context packets, the Reef Engine, and the freshness model. Read these to understand how Mako thinks about a codebase."
  canonicalPath="/docs/concepts/"
  ogImage="/assets/og.png"
  ogType="website"
  breadcrumbs={[{"name": "Home", "href": "/"}, {"name": "Docs", "href": "/docs/"}, {"name": "Concepts", "href": "/docs/concepts/"}]}
>
<header class="doc-page-header">
  <span class="eyebrow">Concepts</span>
    <h1 style="margin-top:1rem;">How <em>agentmako</em> thinks about a codebase.</h1>
    <p class="doc-hero__sub">
      <strong>agentmako</strong> is a local-first MCP server for AI coding
      agents. Four short concept pages explain the model behind it: the
      protocol it speaks, the shape of the context it returns, the durable
      memory layer underneath, and how it tracks what is still fresh.
    </p>
</header>
<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="agents" style="margin-top:1rem;">
      <a class="agent-card" href="./mcp.html">
        <div class="agent-card__head">
          <h3 class="agent-card__name">Model Context Protocol</h3>
          <span class="agent-card__arrow">↗</span>
        </div>
        <div class="agent-card__meta"><span>Concept</span><span>Standard</span></div>
        <p class="agent-card__desc">
          What MCP is, where it came from, and why one server can run
          against every coding agent.
        </p>
      </a>
      <a class="agent-card" href="./context-packets.html">
        <div class="agent-card__head">
          <h3 class="agent-card__name">Context packets</h3>
          <span class="agent-card__arrow">↗</span>
        </div>
        <div class="agent-card__meta"><span>Concept</span><span>Determinism</span></div>
        <p class="agent-card__desc">
          The structured shape returned by <code>context_packet</code> —
          ranked files, related context, active findings, read-next.
        </p>
      </a>
      <a class="agent-card" href="./reef-engine.html">
        <div class="agent-card__head">
          <h3 class="agent-card__name">Reef Engine</h3>
          <span class="agent-card__arrow">↗</span>
        </div>
        <div class="agent-card__meta"><span>Concept</span><span>Memory</span></div>
